children.name: Access while Sat and Sun and midnight

search.queryText:
_sourceCategory=prod/onelogin
| json "event.event_type_id", "event.user_name" as event_id, ユーザー名
| formatDate(_messageTime, "HH") as hour
| formatDate(_messageTime, "EEE") as day
| where ((hour < 5) or (hour > 22) or (day in ("Sat","Sun"))) 
| lookup event_name from onelogin/event_id on event_id = event_id
| formatDate(_messageTime, "MM-dd-yyyy HH:mm:ss") as 日時
| event_name as イベント名
| count by 日時, ユーザー名, イベント名
| urlencode(replace(replace(ユーザー名, " ", "%20"),"　","%20")) as ユーザー名変換後
| if(isEmpty(ユーザー名変換後),tourl(format("https://quocard.jp.sumologic.com/ui/#/dashboardv2/RAtXpSj9SprCfAy7uHJ4cNoc51aHPmOxoMcdbxeCBozHJW4ahP5HtsKhlzIA?variables=User_name:%s",ユーザー名変換後), "」ユーザー名不明"),tourl(format("https://quocard.jp.sumologic.com/ui/#/dashboardv2/RAtXpSj9SprCfAy7uHJ4cNoc51aHPmOxoMcdbxeCBozHJW4ahP5HtsKhlzIA?variables=User_name:%s",ユーザー名変換後), ユーザー名)) as ユーザー名

| if (UserAgent matches "*Windows*" OR UserAgent matches "*Win64*" OR UserAgent matches "*Win32*" OR UserAgent matches "*i686*" OR UserAgent matches "*x86*","PC",type) as type
| if (UserAgent matches "*Macintosh*" OR UserAgent matches "*Mac OS*","Mac",type) as type
| if (type = "","bots/unknown",type) as type

panels.name: Browsers by Workspace
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack (WorkspaceAuditLog OR UserAuditLog OR ChannelAuditLog OR FileAuditLog OR AppAuditLog)
| json "logType", "action", "context.ip_address", "context.ua", "context.location.name", "context.location.type", "actor.user.name", "actor.user.email", "actor.user.id" as LogType, Action, IP, UserAgent, Workspace, Type, User, Email, UserId nodrop
| where !isEmpty(Workspace) and !isEmpty(UserId)
| if (UserAgent matches "*Windows *" OR UserAgent matches "*Win32*" OR UserAgent matches "*Win64*","Windows","") as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "*Macintosh*" OR UserAgent matches "*Darwin/*" OR UserAgent matches "*Mac OS*","MacOS",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "* CrOS *","Chrome OS",OS) as OS
| if (UserAgent matches "*Linux*","Linux",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "*iPad*","iPad",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "*iPhone*","iPhone",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "*Android*","Android",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "*Windows Phone*","Windows Phone",OS) as OS 
| if (OS == "","Other",OS) as OS 
| if (UserAgent matches "Mozilla/*; rv:*)*","Mozilla","") as Browser
| if (UserAgent matches "*MSIE*","Internet Explorer",Browser) as Browser 
| if (UserAgent matches "*Firefox*","Firefox",Browser) as Browser 
| if (UserAgent matches "*Safari*","Safari",Browser) as Browser 
| if (OS=="Android" AND UserAgent matches "*WebKit*","WebKit",Browser) as Browser
| if ((OS=="iPhone" OR OS=="iPad") AND (UserAgent matches "*Mobile/*" OR UserAgent matches "*AppleWebKit*(KHTML*Gecko)*"),"Mobile Safari",Browser) as Browser
| if (browser == "" AND OS=="MacOS" AND UserAgent matches "Mozilla/* (Macintosh;*(KHTML, like Gecko)*","Safari",Browser) as Browser 
| if (UserAgent matches "*MobileSafari/*","Mobile Safari",Browser) as Browser
| if (UserAgent matches "*Chrome*","Chrome",Browser) as Browser 
| if (UserAgent matches "Opera*","Opera",Browser) as Browser 
| if (UserAgent matches "Dolphin*","Dolphin",Browser) as Browser 
| if (Browser == "","Other",Browser) as Browser

panels.name: Threat Location
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"AccessLog"
| json "user_id", "username", "teamName", "count", "ip", "user_agent", "country" as ID, Name, Workspace, Logins, IP, UserAgent, Country nodrop
| withtime Logins
| most_recent(Logins_withtime) as Logins by ID, Name, IP, UserAgent, Workspace
| count by IP
| where !isPrivateIP(IP)
| lookup type, actor, raw, threatlevel as malicious_confidence from sumo://threat/cs on threat=IP 
| json field=raw "labels[*].name" as label_name
| replace(label_name, "\\/","->") as label_name
| replace(label_name, "\""," ") as label_name
| where  type="ip_address" and !isNull(malicious_confidence)
| if (isEmpty(actor), "Unassigned", actor) as Actor
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code from geo://location on ip = IP

panels.name: Desktop OS Version by Workspace

children.name: Slack - Bots
children.description: The Slack - Bots dashboard displays information on bots, which are software applications that run automated tasks over the Internet. Panels show trends by workspace for all bots, active bots, and messages, as well as detailed information on bots, and a detailed bot summary.

panels.name: Instructions
Trend - Bots by Workspace
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"UserLog"
| json "id", "name", "deleted", "real_name", "tz", "tz_label", "is_admin", "is_owner", "is_primary_owner", "is_restricted", "is_ultra_restricted", "is_bot", "is_app_user", "teamName", "billable", "email", "has_2fa" as ID, BotName, Deleted, FullName, TimeZone, TimeZoneLabel, Admin, Owner, PrimaryOwner, Restricted, UltraRestricted, Bot, AppUser, Workspace, Billable, Email, AuthenticationEnabled nodrop
| where Deleted matches "false" and (Bot matches "true" OR BotName matches "slackbot")
| timeslice 24h
| withtime ID
| most_recent(ID_withtime) as Bots by _timeslice, Workspace, ID
| count by _timeslice, Workspace
| transpose row _timeslice column Workspace

panels.name: Trend - Active Bots by Workspace
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "user", "userName", "type", "subType", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName" as ID, BotName, Type, SubType, MessageTime, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace nodrop
| where [subquery:"logType":"UserLog"
| json "id", "name", "deleted", "is_bot", "teamName" as ID, Name, Deleted, Bot, Workspace nodrop
| where (Bot matches "true" OR Name matches "slackbot") and Deleted matches "false"
| withtime Name
| most_recent(Name_withtime) as Name by ID, Workspace
| compose ID, Workspace]
| timeslice 10m
| count_distinct(ID) by Workspace, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column Workspace
| fillmissing timeslice(10m)

| json "user", "userName", "type", "subType", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName" as ID, BotName, Type, SubType, MessageTime, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace nodrop

panels.name: Bot Summary
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack
| join ("logType":"ConversationLog" | json "user", "userName", "type", "subtype", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName" as ID, User, Type, SubType, Time, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace nodrop
| count_distinct(Time) as Messages by ID, User, Channel, Workspace) as T1,
("logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "user", "teamName", "files", "channelId" as ID, Workspace, Files, channelID nodrop
| parse regex field=Files "(?<File>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi nodrop
| json field=File "name" as FileName nodrop
| count_distinct(FileName) as TotalFiles by Workspace, ID, channelID
| sum(TotalFiles) as TotalFiles by Workspace, ID) as T2 , ("logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "user", "teamName", "attachments", "channelId" as ID, Workspace, Attachments, ChannelID nodrop
| parse regex field=Attachments "(?<Attachment>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi nodrop
| json field=Attachment "fallback" as fallback nodrop
| count_distinct(fallback) as TotalAttachments by Workspace, ID, ChannelID
| sum(TotalAttachments) as TotalAttachments by Workspace, ID) as T3 on T1.ID = T2.ID and T2.ID = T3.ID and T1.Workspace=T2.Workspace and T2.Workspace=T3.Workspace
| T1_Workspace as Workspace | T1_ID as ID| T1_User as BotName | T1_Channel as Channel
| where Workspace matches {{Workspace}} and Channel matches {{Channel}} and BotName matches {{BotName}}
| T2_TotalFiles as %"Total Files"| T3_TotalAttachments as %"Total Attachments"
| where [subquery:"logType":"UserLog"
| json "id", "name", "deleted", "is_bot", "teamName" as ID, Name, Deleted, Bot, Workspace nodrop
| where (Bot matches "true" or Name matches "slackbot") and Deleted matches "false"
| withtime Name
| most_recent(Name_withtime) as Name by ID, Workspace
| compose ID, Workspace]
| count_distinct(channel) as %"Number of Channels", sum(T1_Messages) as %"Total Messages"  by Workspace, BotName,  %"Total Files", %"Total Attachments"
| fields Workspace, BotName, %"Number of Channels", %"Total Messages", %"Total Files", %"Total Attachments"
| sort by %"Total Messages"
| limit 20

("logType":"ConversationLog"

panels.name: Channels
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"channelDetail"
| json "channel_id", "teamName" as ChannelId, Workspace
| timeslice 1h
| withtime ChannelId
| most_recent(ChannelId_withtime) as ChannelId by ChannelId, Workspace, _timeslice
| count as %"Number of Channels" by Workspace, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column Workspace

panels.name: Active Channels
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "channelId", "teamName" as ChannelId, Workspace
| timeslice 1h
| withtime ChannelId
| most_recent(ChannelId_withtime) as ChannelId by ChannelId, Workspace, _timeslice
| count as %"Number of Channels" by Workspace, _timeslice
| transpose row _timeslice column Workspace
| fillmissing timeslice(1h)

panels.name: In-Active Channels
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"channelDetail"
| json "channel_name", "channel_id", "teamName", "members" as Channel, ChannelId, Workspace, Members
| withtime ChannelId
| most_recent(ChannelId_withtime) as ChannelId by Channel, ChannelId, Workspace, Members
| where ![subquery: "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "channelId", "teamName" as ChannelId, Workspace  
| withtime ChannelId
| most_recent(ChannelId_withtime) as ChannelId by ChannelId, Workspace 
| compose ChannelId, Workspace]
| where Channel matches {{Channel}} and Workspace matches {{Workspace}}
| sort by Members asc
| fields Workspace, Channel, Members

panels.name: Top 10 Channels by Files
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "channelId", "teamName", "files", "channelName" as ChannelId, Workspace, Files, Channel nodrop
| parse regex field=Files "(?<File>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi nodrop
| json field=File "name" as FileName nodrop
| where Channel matches {{Channel}} and Workspace matches {{Workspace}}
| count_distinct(FileName) as TotalFiles by Workspace, ChannelId, Channel
| where TotalFiles > 0
| fields Workspace, Channel, TotalFiles
| sort by TotalFiles
| limit 10

panels.name: Top 10 Channels by Attachments
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "channelId", "teamName", "attachments", "channelName" as ChannelId, Workspace, Attachments, Channel nodrop
| parse regex field=Attachments "(?<Attachment>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi nodrop
| json field=Attachment "fallback" as AttachmentName nodrop
| where Channel matches {{Channel}} and Workspace matches {{Workspace}}
| count_distinct(AttachmentName) as TotalAttachments by Workspace, ChannelId, Channel
| where TotalAttachments > 0
| fields Workspace, Channel, TotalAttachments
| sort by TotalAttachments
| limit 10

panels.name: Channel Summary
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack
| join ("logType":"channelDetail"
| json "channel_name", "channel_id", "teamName", "members" as Channel, ChannelId, Workspace, Members
| withtime Members
| most_recent(Members_withtime) as Members by Channel, ChannelId, Workspace) as T1,("logType":"ConversationLog" | json "user", "userName", "type", "subtype", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName" as ID, User, Type, SubType, Time, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace nodrop
| count_distinct(Time) as Messages by ID, ChannelId, Workspace) as T2 on T1.ChannelId = T2.ChannelId and T1.Workspace=T2.Workspace
| T2_Workspace as Workspace | T2_ID as User| T1_Channel as Channel
| where Workspace matches {{Workspace}} and Channel matches {{Channel}}
| T1_Members as %"Team Members"
| fields Workspace, Channel, User, %"Team Members" ,T2_Messages
| where [subquery:"logType":"UserLog"
| json "id", "name", "deleted", "is_bot", "teamName" as User, Name, Deleted, Bot, Workspace nodrop
| where Bot matches "false" and !(Name matches "slackbot") and Deleted matches "false"
| withtime Name
| most_recent(Name_withtime) as Name by User, Workspace
| compose User, Workspace]
| sum(T2_Messages) as %"Total Messages", count_distinct(User) as %"Members Posted Messages" by Workspace, Channel, %"Team Members"
| fields Workspace, Channel, %"Team Members", %"Total Messages", %"Members Posted Messages"
| sort by %"Total Messages"
| limit 20

panels.name: Total File Size
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "userName", "type", "subtype", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName", "files" as User, Type, SubType, MessageTime, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace, Files nodrop
| where !isEmpty(Files)
| parse regex field=Files "(?<File>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi
| json field=File "name", "fileSize", "fileType" as FileName, FileSize, FileType
| sum(FileSize) as TotalInBytes
| TotalInBytes/1024/1024 as TotalInMB
| fields TotalInMB

panels.name: Recent Attachments
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory = prod/slack "logType":"ConversationLog"
| json "userName", "type", "subtype", "ts", "text", "channelId", "channelName", "teamName", "attachments", "user" as User, Type, SubType, MessageTime, Text, ChannelId, Channel, Workspace, Attachments, ID nodrop
| where !isEmpty(Attachments)
| if (isEmpty(User), ID, User) as User
| parse regex field=Attachments "(?<Attachment>\{[^\}]+(?:\}\}|\}))" multi
| json field=Attachment "id", "text", "author_name", "author_link", "pretext", "fallback" as AttachmentId, AttachementText, AuthorName, AuthorLink, PreText, Fallback nodrop
| if (isEmpty(AuthorName), "-", AuthorName) as AuthorName
| where [subquery from=(-24h):"logType":"UserLog"
| json "id", "name", "deleted", "is_bot", "teamName", "is_restricted", "is_ultra_restricted" as ID, Name, Deleted, Bot, Workspace, is_restricted, is_ultra_restricted nodrop
| where is_restricted matches {{Restricted}} OR is_ultra_restricted matches {{UltraRestricted}}
| withtime Name
| most_recent(Name_withtime) as Name by ID, Workspace
| compose ID, Workspace]
| where Workspace matches {{Workspace}} and Channel matches {{Channel}} and AttachementText matches {{AttachementText}} and AuthorName matches {{AuthorName}} and User matches {{User}}
| formatDate(fromMillis(toLong(MessageTime*1000)),"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS ZZZZ") as Time
| AttachementText as %"Attachement Text" 
| AuthorName as %"Author Name"
| tourl(AuthorLink, "Author Link") as %"Author Link"
| count as Count by Time, Workspace, Channel, User, Text, %"Attachement Text", Fallback, PreText, AuthorName, %"Author Link"
| sort by Time
| limit 20
| fields - Count

| json field=File "name", "fileSize", "fileType", "urlPrivate", "permalink", "urlPrivateDownload" as FileName, FileSize, FileType, PrivateURL, PermanentLink, URLDownload nodrop
| where [subquery from=(-24h):"logType":"UserLog"

| where is_restricted matches {{Restricted}} OR is_ultra_restricted matches {{UltraRestricted}}
| withtime Name
| most_recent(Name_withtime) as Name by ID, Workspace

| FileName as %"File Name"| FileSize as %"File Size"| FileType as %"File Type"| tourl(PrivateURL, "Private URL") as %"Private URL"
| tourl(PermanentLink, "Permanent Link") as %"Permanent Link" | tourl(URLDownload, "Download Link") as %"Download Link"
| formatDate(fromMillis(toLong(MessageTime*1000)),"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS ZZZZ") as Time
| count as Count by Time, Workspace, Channel, User, Text, %"File Name", %"File Size", %"File Type", %"Private URL", %"Permanent Link", %"Download Link"
